SELECT c.relname AS index_name, r.relname AS table_name, i.indkey AS ind_keys FROM pg_catalog.pg_class c, pg_catalog.pg_namespace n, pg_catalog.pg_index i, pg_catalog.pg_class r WHERE c.relkind = $2 AND c.relnamespace = n.oid AND n.nspname = $1 AND c.oid = i.indexrelid AND r.oid = i.indrelid
